songs.title: Feelin’ Freaky
songs.lyrics:

[Omarion]
B2K and Nick Cannon
Trackmasters

My style is powder blue

'Cause after the party you dont have to call me
'Cause Can' is the prodigy and I mobs deep

You do it in the closet, you know you think Im handsome
Yeah, the kid's real attractive
